{"tid":1130371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山男子租車燒炭死亡","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T04:01:35.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcc86c5c09a705298a184a6d30afb4ff6375d98","tid":1130371,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/photo/bkn-20190429085115031-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190429104327\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190429085115031-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190429104327&h=c8dcfb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早(29日)8時18分，有途人行經馬鞍山村路時，發現一名年約60歲男子，昏迷一輛私家車的司機位上，由於昨日已見該車停泊在上址，感到事有蹺蹊報警。警方及救護員趕至，證實司機已氣絕身亡，並且在車廂內發現有燒過的木炭，相信他燒炭自殺，並且檢獲懷疑遺書，正聯絡其家人助查。<br />\n<br />\n警方根據車牌資料追查，證實該車屬於一間租車公司，由事主早前租用。"},{"pid":"c643ce549187da0b2cd1f5ce2c63a47a8f2014b0","tid":1130371,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"識玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33b5924fda72d0a25cf08a6cd3379a8f76c5eec","tid":1130371,"uid":182406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrip"},{"pid":"a61773d2e4a64ab6e9c4293bf04053d7c41e2e8b","tid":1130371,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下手租車條友真係祝佢好運"},{"pid":"4609e8b2f730451bacc2df4394c7c086e12b22e3","tid":1130371,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:01:35.000Z","msg":"好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}